<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <% if @payment_info_needed %>
      <p>
        This is a friendly heads up that the trial period for your Badge List group 
        (<%= link_to @group.name, group_url(@group) %>)
        ends in <%= pluralize @days_until_end, 'day' %>.  To continue using the group
        you'll need to add a credit card to your account by clicking the link below.
      </p>
      <p>
        <%= link_to 'Add a card to your account', 
          edit_user_registration_url + '?d=ac#add-card' %>
      </p>
    <% else %>
      <p>
        This is a friendly heads up that the trial period for your Badge List group 
        (<%= link_to @group.name, group_url(@group) %>)
        ends in <%= pluralize @days_until_end, 'day' %>.  At the end of trial period your card
        will be billed for your first month's service.
      </p>
    <% end %>
    
    <p>
      <strong>Have any questions?</strong>
      Try checking out the <a href="https://www.badgelist.com/help/docs">help documentation</a>
      and earning some badges in the 
      <a href="https://www.badgelist.com/community">Badge List Community</a>.
      You can also email us at 
      <a href="mailto:solutions@badgelist.com">solutions@badgelist.com</a>. 
    </p>

    <p>
      Thanks for using Badge List!
    </p>

    <hr/>
    <p>
      <i>
        This email was sent automatically by the Badge List app.
      </i>
    </p>
  </body>
</html>